          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " A 13.8 MeV F-18 radioactive beam which was produced",
                "using the ISOL technique. A first cyclotron, CYCLONE 30",
                "delivers protons of 15.5 MeV on the production target",
                "which consists in a 1 cm**3 of water enriched in O-18.",
                "The F-18 beam is then produced through the",
                "O-18(p,n)F-18 exchange charge reaction. Then the F-18",
                "beam accelerated to the relevant energy with the",
                "CYCLONE 110 cyclotron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.In the present experiment, the O-18",
                "content was evaluated using the difference of the",
                "energy loss between F-18 and O-18 in a thick aluminum",
                "foil, approx. 670 mug/cm** thick, placed before the",
                "target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 70 mug/cm**2 polyethylene CH2 targets was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 18-F radioactive beam, ionized to 2+ state."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Alpha-particles were detected in coincidence",
                "with O-15 ions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The framework of the R-matrix model."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The products of the H(F-18,a)O-15 reaction were",
                "detected using the multi-strip silicon detector LEDA.",
                "These detectors are composed of 8 sectors, each",
                "divided into 16 radial strips.",
                "The energy calibration of the 256 strips was performed",
                "with a calibrated 3 alpha-source(Pu-239, Am-241 and",
                "Cm-244) whereas the TOF calibration was performed with",
                "a precision pulse generator."
              ]
            }
          ],
